Ribamar Changelog

[BC]: Breaking Change
[NF]: New Functionality
[BF]: Bug Fix

2018-10-01 [v0.1.0]
- Fix deprecated codeclimate settings.
- Add support for mongodb authentication [NF].
- Improve Ribamar CLI.
- Fix some unhandled exceptions [BF].
- API: Renamed Credential "id" to "key" in order to prevent confusion [BC].
- Add setting to define if a account field is an e-mail address [NF].
- API: Add method for relaying e-mails to accounts [NF].

2018-09-17 [v0.0.1]
- First officialy published version.
